<h2>🟢 4. Bookstore &amp; E-Commerce Module</h2>
<p><strong>Objective:</strong> Test the full shopping cart and checkout pipeline.</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="left">Test ID</th>
<th align="left">Action to Perform</th>
<th align="left">Expected Result</th>
