</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="left">SHOP-01</td>
<td align="left">Go to <strong>Bookstore</strong>. Use the category filter buttons at the top.</td>
<td align="left">The book list filters to show only books matching the selected category.</td>
<td align="left"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">SHOP-02</td>
<td align="left">Click &quot;Add to Cart&quot; on two different books.</td>
<td align="left">The cart notification pops up, and the cart icon counter updates.</td>
<td align="left"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">SHOP-03</td>
<td align="left">Click the cart icon to open the shopping cart sidebar.</td>
<td align="left">The selected books are listed with correct prices. The subtotal is accurately calculated.</td>
<td align="left"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">SHOP-04</td>
<td align="left">Click &quot;Proceed to Checkout&quot;. Fill in dummy payment details and submit.</td>
<td align="left">The payment processes and redirects to the Order Confirmation page.</td>
<td align="left"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">SHOP-05</td>
<td align="left">On the Order Confirmation page, click &quot;Download Receipt (PDF)&quot;.</td>
<td align="left">A PDF receipt is generated and downloaded to the computer with the correct order details.</td>
<td align="left"></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
