<tbody><tr>
<td align="left">FORUM-01</td>
<td align="left">Go to <strong>Forum</strong>. Type a question in the &quot;Ask a Question&quot; box and submit.</td>
<td align="left">The question instantly appears at the top of the discussion feed.</td>
<td align="left"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">FORUM-02</td>
<td align="left">Click the &quot;Like&quot; (Heart) button on any post.</td>
<td align="left">The like count increases by 1 and the heart turns red.</td>
<td align="left"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">FORUM-03</td>
<td align="left">Click the &quot;Like&quot; button again on the same post.</td>
<td align="left">The like is cancelled (count decreases by 1) and the heart turns grey.</td>
<td align="left"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">FORUM-04</td>
<td align="left">Type a reply in the &quot;Write a reply...&quot; input box of a post.</td>
<td align="left">The reply is appended under the post.</td>
<td align="left"></td>
</tr>
