<h2>🟢 6. Admin Portal &amp; System Control</h2>
<p><strong>Objective:</strong> Test the administrative capabilities for data management.</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="left">Test ID</th>
<th align="left">Action to Perform</th>
<th align="left">Expected Result</th>
